<p align=left><font face="Arial" color=#ff0000 size=2>THE SOUND VIEW EXTENSION:</font><font face="Arial" size=2> A proposed southern extension of the Bronx River Parkway into Sound View Park, with an additional interchange at Randall Avenue, remained an active plan until the early 1970s. The right-of-way for the proposed extension has since been incorporated into Sound View Park.</font><font face="Times New Roman" size=2><br></font>
</td>
